init_text: You're Barack Obama. 4 years into your retirement, you awake to find a letter with no return address on your bedside table. It reads "I hope you've had a chance to relax Barack...but pack your bags and call the number below. It's time to start the real job." Signed simply, "JFK."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You call the number and are greeted by a man with a thick Russian accent.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You arrive at the coffee shop and are greeted by a man who looks like he's been on the wrong side of a few too many bar fights.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "He needs you to be the President again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He agrees to take the job.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Welcome to the team Barack." said JFK.
